WEBVTT

00:01:27.790 --> 00:01:32.887
suv toshqini, zilzila, vulqon otilishi, 
qurg'oqchilik va boshqalar.

00:01:32.887 --> 00:01:35.607
Xo'sh, ularning soni qanchalik o'zgardi?

00:01:35.607 --> 00:01:39.093
Gapminder tashkiloti 
Shvetsiya aholisidan so'rov o'tkazdi.

00:01:39.093 --> 00:01:40.952
Mana ularning javoblari.

00:01:40.952 --> 00:01:42.881
Shved jamoatchiligi
shunday javob berdi:

00:01:42.881 --> 00:01:44.353
ularning 50 foizi ikki baravar

00:01:44.353 --> 00:01:46.558
ko'paydi deb o'ylagan, 38 %i 
deyarli o'zgarmay

00:01:46.558 --> 00:01:48.656
qoldi, 12 %iga ko'ra, 
ikki marta qisqargan.

00:01:48.656 --> 00:01:51.308
Bu tadqiqotchilar tomonidan 
yig'ilgan eng ishonchli

00:01:51.308 --> 00:01:54.274
ma'lumotlardir, ularning soni goh 
ko'tariladi, goh tushadi,

00:01:54.274 --> 00:01:56.826
II Jahon urushida
eng yuqori ko'rsatichni qayd etgach,

00:01:56.826 --> 00:02:00.226
u pasaya boshladi